{
  "senderAccountId": 6,
  "receiverAccountId": 5,
  "amount": 100
}

### negative: user cannot transfer to non-existing account

POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/transfer
Authorization: Basic YW5uYTE5OTY6UGFzc3dvcmQxIQ==
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderAccountId": 4,
  "receiverAccountId": 100,
  "amount": 200
}

### negative: user cannot transfer from non-existing account

POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/transfer
Authorization: Basic YW5uYTE5OTY6UGFzc3dvcmQxIQ==
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderAccountId": 100,
  "receiverAccountId": 5,
  "amount": 200
}

### negative: unauthorized user cannot transfer

POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderAccountId": 4,
  "receiverAccountId": 5,
  "amount": 200
}

### negative: user with invalid auth cannot transfer

POST http://localhost:4111/api/v1/accounts/transfer
